的收缩期喷射样杂音，可伴震颤，为左室流出道梗阻所致。 梗阻性心肌病患者因血流经过狭窄处时的漏斗效应，吸引二尖瓣前叶收缩期前向运动，贴近室间隔，可进一步加重左室流出道梗阻，同时出现二尖瓣关闭不全，在心尖可闻及全收缩期吹风样杂音。超声心动图：室间隔显著增厚，舒张期末的室间隔厚度＞15mm 或与后壁厚度之比＞1.3; 左室流出道狭窄;二尖瓣前叶收缩期前向运动;主动脉瓣收缩中期提前关闭。心尖肥厚型心肌病可见心尖室间隔和左室后下壁明显肥厚。</span></p><p><br/></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":5088,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","updateTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2159,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">风湿性心脏病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5089,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","updateTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2159,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">病毒性心肌炎</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5090,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","updateTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2159,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">高血压性心脏损害</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5091,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","updateTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","isTrue":false,"questionId":2159,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">扩张型心肌病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":5092,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","updateTime":"2019-06-19 17:12:55","isTrue":true,"questionId":2159,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">肥厚型心肌病</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":939,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:30:46","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:30:46","name":"心血管A3","questionCnt":8,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":931,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:38","name":"161","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}